mylistpackage

Class AbstractLinkedArrayMyList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • mylistpackage.AbstractLinkedArrayMyList<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the data type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    MyList<E>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LinkedArrayListSorted, LinkedArrayListUnsorted

    public abstract class AbstractLinkedArrayMyList<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements MyList<E>
    Abstract class for all LinkedArrayList data structures. The underlying data structure is an array, but the entity can be operated on same as a linked list. This implies the array is re-sizable.
    Version:
    4.16C
    Author:
    Sam Brendel
